1858
01:09:11,771 --> 01:09:15,210
(After cleaning up for 3 straight days, you'd get used to it.)

1859
01:09:15,211 --> 01:09:18,010
Fresh manure is definitely easier to push.

1860
01:09:18,011 --> 01:09:20,911
- Right?
- It's satisfying.

1861
01:09:21,411 --> 01:09:23,551
How does fresh manure feel different?

1862
01:09:24,751 --> 01:09:25,751
Fresh manure?

1863
01:09:27,921 --> 01:09:29,061
It feels lighter.

1864
01:09:30,861 --> 01:09:32,631
Old manure gets...

1865
01:09:33,461 --> 01:09:34,691
really hard...

1866
01:09:37,501 --> 01:09:38,571
and dry.

1867
01:09:39,471 --> 01:09:44,171
You have to break it up first to clean it up.

1868
01:09:45,071 --> 01:09:49,341
But fresh one just slides away with a little push.

1869
01:09:49,711 --> 01:09:51,810
(Woo Bin became a manure master.)

1870
01:09:51,811 --> 01:09:53,681
- Let's milk them right away.
- All right.

1871
01:09:54,011 --> 01:09:55,851
We're working faster than yesterday.

1872
01:09:56,751 --> 01:09:57,780
Right?

1873
01:09:57,781 --> 01:09:59,020
(The milking barn is cleaned in no time.)

1874
01:09:59,021 --> 01:10:00,291
Come on.

1875
01:10:00,591 --> 01:10:03,061
Let's feed the baby cows.

1876
01:10:05,361 --> 01:10:06,831
Your leg looks better now.

1877
01:10:07,461 --> 01:10:08,461
(Farting)

1878
01:10:08,462 --> 01:10:09,761
Stop farting.

1879
01:10:11,001 --> 01:10:12,301
She's pooping right away.

1880
01:10:14,331 --> 01:10:16,401
Yes, poop as much as you want.

1881
01:10:18,241 --> 01:10:21,781
(Milking begins as the cows enjoy their special feed.)

1882
01:10:21,941 --> 01:10:25,850
The high-producing ones took about 7 to 8 minutes yesterday.

1883
01:10:25,851 --> 01:10:27,980
- Right.
- Clearly...

1884
01:10:27,981 --> 01:10:29,050
(While they're milking for the calves)

1885
01:10:29,051 --> 01:10:30,051
Kwang Soo.

1886
01:10:31,221 --> 01:10:32,221
Yes?

1887
01:10:32,222 --> 01:10:33,790
(Kyung Soo checks in on Kwang Soo's team.)

1888
01:10:33,791 --> 01:10:35,121
Kwang Soo must be done by now.

1889
01:10:35,961 --> 01:10:37,090
