- Okay.

1893
01:10:43,461 --> 01:10:45,500
While you give this bag...

1894
01:10:45,501 --> 01:10:47,300
- up to here, - Yes.

1895
01:10:47,301 --> 01:10:49,040
I'll start there and go all the way.

1896
01:10:49,041 --> 01:10:50,041
All right.

1897
01:10:50,042 --> 01:10:52,740
CEO Lee seems to know what to do.

1898
01:10:52,741 --> 01:10:53,841
- Really?
- Yes.

1899
01:10:54,141 --> 01:10:56,310
Including which buttons to press,

1900
01:10:56,311 --> 01:10:59,011
he knows what to do.

1901
01:10:59,111 --> 01:11:01,180
(Laughing)

1902
01:11:01,181 --> 01:11:03,681
I don't think he needs us anymore.

1903
01:11:03,881 --> 01:11:04,981
- Really?
- Yes.

1904
01:11:05,791 --> 01:11:08,150
CEO Lee, you work very neatly.

1905
01:11:08,151 --> 01:11:09,961
- Right?
- You're doing a good job.

1906
01:11:10,461 --> 01:11:12,190
Please remember that.

1907
01:11:12,191 --> 01:11:14,260
- Okay.
- How well I work.

1908
01:11:14,261 --> 01:11:16,530
I stopped myself...

1909
01:11:16,531 --> 01:11:17,730
