1944
01:12:45,821 --> 01:12:46,821
Come this way.

1945
01:12:48,251 --> 01:12:49,361
Farmfarm.

1946
01:12:50,191 --> 01:12:51,221
Here you go.

1947
01:12:52,131 --> 01:12:54,390
(Farmfarm's drinking milk can't be missed.)

1948
01:12:54,391 --> 01:12:56,161
Their personality is different.

1949
01:12:57,301 --> 01:12:59,030
- Doesn't he pull the bottle a lot?
- He was born...

1950
01:12:59,031 --> 01:13:00,901
He was born not so long ago,

1951
01:13:01,371 --> 01:13:02,401
