1954
01:13:08,111 --> 01:13:10,340
Gogo, you're done eating.

1955
01:13:10,341 --> 01:13:11,741
Thank you for the food.

1956
01:13:12,381 --> 01:13:13,451
You're done.

1957
01:13:13,851 --> 01:13:15,750
