1958
01:13:15,751 --> 01:13:17,021
Is it delicious?

1959
01:13:17,421 --> 01:13:19,650
(Patting)

1960
01:13:19,651 --> 01:13:21,551
Have some more. Drink it all.

1961
01:13:22,961 --> 01:13:23,961
Drink it all.

1962
01:13:23,962 --> 01:13:25,961
