1976
01:13:58,061 --> 01:13:59,161
Even the grazing?

1977
01:13:59,261 --> 01:14:00,461
I think they can manage.

1978
01:14:02,031 --> 01:14:03,961
It's easy as long as the cows move smoothly.

1979
01:14:05,231 --> 01:14:06,730
They're still taking a break.

1980
01:14:06,731 --> 01:14:07,971
