1981
01:14:08,071 --> 01:14:10,441
Hey.

1982
01:14:12,211 --> 01:14:13,311
Let's go.

1983
01:14:14,241 --> 01:14:17,010
Let's go and play.

1984
01:14:17,011 --> 01:14:18,410
