(Yodeling)

1993
01:14:35,661 --> 01:14:36,700
That's not the way.

1994
01:14:36,701 --> 01:14:38,870
- No.
- Come on, everyone.

1995
01:14:38,871 --> 01:14:41,031
- It's this way.
- Let's go and have fun.

1996
01:14:41,801 --> 01:14:43,741
Come. Let's go.

1997
01:14:44,071 --> 01:14:45,071
Go.

1998
01:14:45,072 --> 01:14:46,970
(It's their 4th time, so this is a piece of cake.)

1999
01:14:46,971 --> 01:14:48,881
Let's go.

2000
01:14:49,641 --> 01:14:52,450
(At that moment...)

2001
01:14:52,451 --> 01:14:54,780
(The students escape within 1 minute.)

2002
01:14:54,781 --> 01:14:56,181
No, that's not the way.

2003
01:14:57,021 --> 01:14:58,121
Go.

2004
01:14:58,481 --> 01:14:59,750
(Yodeling)

2005
01:14:59,751 --> 01:15:02,121
(No matter how much they call them)

2006
01:15:02,221 --> 01:15:03,560
Let's go.

2007
01:15:03,561 --> 01:15:05,760
Let's go. No. Go.

2008
01:15:05,761 --> 01:15:09,261
Move forward. Go.

2009
01:15:09,361 --> 01:15:10,701
Let's go.

2010
01:15:11,531 --> 01:15:12,931
Let's go. Why aren't you moving?

2011
01:15:14,131 --> 01:15:17,141
- Let's go.
- Hey, come on.

2012
01:15:17,241 --> 01:15:19,741
(Some of them say hello to the calves.)

2013
01:15:20,371 --> 01:15:21,371
Hey.

2014
01:15:21,372 --> 01:15:22,811
(Some students go back home.)

2015
01:15:23,081 --> 01:15:25,581
Come on. Let's go and have fun.

2016
01:15:26,011 --> 01:15:27,151
Can you move out of the way?

2017
01:15:27,851 --> 01:15:28,880
No.

2018
01:15:28,881 --> 01:15:30,220
That's not the way.

2019
01:15:30,221 --> 01:15:33,290
