2041
01:16:09,561 --> 01:16:12,630
(Back to the complete mess)

2042
01:16:12,631 --> 01:16:16,130
Let's go.

2043
01:16:16,131 --> 01:16:18,130
(Teacher Moon shouts without hesitation.)

2044
01:16:18,131 --> 01:16:20,531
No, you can't go there.

2045
01:16:20,901 --> 01:16:23,601
- Let's go.
- No, wait.

2046
01:16:23,701 --> 01:16:26,410
It's not this way.

2047
01:16:26,411 --> 01:16:27,440
(Kyung Soo is busy pulling the cart and keeping the students in order.)

2048
01:16:27,441 --> 01:16:28,511
It's that way.

2049
01:16:29,481 --> 01:16:30,580
