2050
01:16:30,581 --> 01:16:31,641
That's it.

2051
01:16:32,851 --> 01:16:34,181
It will work out somehow.

2052
01:16:35,721 --> 01:16:36,750
Go.

2053
01:16:36,751 --> 01:16:38,121
(The vice principal is positive about everything.)

2054
01:16:38,381 --> 01:16:39,691
Let's go.

2055
01:16:40,251 --> 01:16:41,890
Come on, let's go.

2056
01:16:41,891 --> 01:16:42,990
(The finish line is finally in sight.)

2057
01:16:42,991 --> 01:16:46,790
(Satisfied by how the trainees graze the cows)

2058
01:16:46,791 --> 01:16:47,991
He's also funny.

2059
01:16:48,491 --> 01:16:50,930
The guy in the straw hat.

2060
01:16:50,931 --> 01:16:51,960
Why?

2061
01:16:51,961 --> 01:16:53,471
He's just funny.

2062
01:16:54,431 --> 01:16:56,370
(Yodeling)

2063
01:16:56,371 --> 01:16:58,911
(He seems to like KKPP's yodeling.)

2064
01:16:59,511 --> 01:17:01,540
- Hey.
- Let's go.

2065
01:17:01,541 --> 01:17:03,040
That's right.

2066
01:17:03,041 --> 01:17:04,041
Let's close it.

2067
01:17:04,041 --> 01:17:05,041
(Once all the students are inside,)

2068
01:17:06,811 --> 01:17:10,580
(the teachers lock the gate.)

2069
01:17:10,581 --> 01:17:14,790
