2070
01:17:14,791 --> 01:17:17,791
- Well done, everyone.
- Well done.

2071
01:17:17,921 --> 01:17:19,090
Isn't it less tiring...

2072
01:17:19,091 --> 01:17:20,231
- than yesterday?
- Yes.

2073
01:17:20,631 --> 01:17:22,061
It feels like we're getting used to the work.

2074
01:17:22,601 --> 01:17:24,360
(They grab their things from the hut.)

2075
01:17:24,361 --> 01:17:26,101
I think I need to put eye drops in my eyes one more time.

2076
01:17:26,831 --> 01:17:28,000
- Kwang Soo, let's go.
- Okay.

2077
01:17:28,001 --> 01:17:29,001
What are they?

2078
01:17:29,002 --> 01:17:31,000
Good job on the morning task.

2079
01:17:31,001 --> 01:17:33,210
You're going to take a rest now.

2080
01:17:33,211 --> 01:17:35,010
- Okay.
