2100
01:18:12,711 --> 01:18:14,350
(like this?)

2101
01:18:14,351 --> 01:18:15,850
(Do you know how to make curry or not?)

2102
01:18:15,851 --> 01:18:18,121
(Well, I...)

2103
01:18:18,321 --> 01:18:19,950
(Stop giving orders...)

2104
01:18:19,951 --> 01:18:22,321
(and just follow Doh Kyung Soo's instructions.)

2105
01:18:22,591 --> 01:18:24,821
(Moon Sang Hoon can't do anything.)

2106
01:18:25,021 --> 01:18:27,531
(Will the head chef finish making curry under pressure?)

2107
01:18:27,591 --> 01:18:28,591
It's really big here.

2108
01:18:28,592 --> 01:18:31,561
(And KKPP's second training site)

2109
01:18:31,801 --> 01:18:33,471
(Laughing)

